## MPL syntax highlighting

syntax "MPL" "\.mpl$"
comment "#"

color green "\<(start|end|print|int|float|string|funct|if|else|while|for)\>"
color brightmagenta "\<(return)\>"
color magenta "[(){}]"
color yellow "[.:;,+*|=!<>&]"
color brightred ""(\\.|[^"])*""
color brightblue "#.*"
color ,green "[[:space:]]+$"
